{
  "viz_type": "funnel",
  "display_name": "Funnel Chart",
  "purpose": "第三方 embedding / guest token 场景下安全传输的 Funnel Chart form_data 模板",
  "base_form_data_schema_file": "D:/vsx/metrics/supersonic/form-data-schema/funnel-form-data-schema.json",
  "source_files": [
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset/security/manager.py",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset/constants.py",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset/utils/core.py",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset/charts/data/api.py",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset/commands/chart/data/get_data_command.py",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset/charts/schemas.py",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-core/src/query/constants.ts",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-core/src/query/types/QueryFormData.ts",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-core/src/query/processExtraFormData.ts",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Funnel/buildQuery.ts",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Funnel/transformProps.ts",
    "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/utils/eventHandlers.ts"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "embedded guest 的核心限制在后端 `security/manager.py::query_context_modified()`。报错原文是 `Guest user cannot modify chart payload`。",
    "Funnel 是标准 chart data API 图表。guest 请求的安全做法不是重新拼装一份新的 funnel form_data，而是以已保存图表的 form_data 原样复制为 base，只把动态条件放进 extra_form_data。",
    "对 Funnel 而言，最敏感的根字段是 `metric`、`groupby` 和 `sort_by_metric`，因为它们会直接影响 query_context.queries[*].metrics / columns / orderby。",
    "Funnel 的交互筛选形状已经在 `utils/eventHandlers.ts` 中明确：点击 step 后，会按 `groupby` 各列生成 `extraFormData.filters=[{col:<groupby_col>, op:'IN', val:[...]}]`。",
    "当前 Funnel controlPanel 不包含正式时间字段，所以 guest embedding 的动态入口主要应是 `extra_form_data.filters` 与 `extra_form_data.adhoc_filters`，而不是时间 override。"
  ],
  "security_enforcement": {
    "backend_check_function": "superset/security/manager.py::query_context_modified",
    "checked_when": "ChartDataCommand.validate() -> QueryContext.raise_for_access()",
    "error_message": "Guest user cannot modify chart payload",
    "hard_block_fields": [
      "slice_id",
      "metrics",
      "groupby",
      "columns",
      "orderby"
    ],
    "indirectly_sensitive_fields_for_funnel": [
      "metric",
      "groupby",
      "sort_by_metric"
    ],
    "recommended_strategy": "复制保存态 chart form_data 作为 base，仅通过 extra_form_data 追加过滤条件。"
  },
  "safe_base_rule": {
    "description": "第三方 embedding 请求中的根层 form_data，应当从已保存 Funnel 图表的 form_data 直接复制，不要重构。",
    "must_be_copied_from_saved_chart": [
      "slice_id",
      "datasource",
      "viz_type",
      "metric",
      "groupby",
      "adhoc_filters",
      "row_limit",
      "sort_by_metric",
      "percent_calculation_type",
      "color_scheme",
      "show_legend",
      "legendOrientation",
      "legendMargin",
      "label_type",
      "tooltip_label_type",
      "number_format",
      "currency_format",
      "show_labels",
      "show_tooltip_labels",
      "all other chart-definition fields"
    ],
    "why": [
      "`query_context_modified()` 会把请求中的 metrics/groupby/columns/orderby 与保存态图表对比。",
      "Funnel 的 `metric` 会进入 query.metrics，`groupby` 会进入 query.columns，`sort_by_metric` 会决定 query.orderby 是否存在。",
      "guest 模式下，即使只是为了嵌入联动筛选，也不应在根层主动改这些图表定义字段。"
    ]
  },
  "safe_embedding_form_data_template": {
    "description": "这是 guest embedding 下的安全写法。根层以保存态 Funnel 图表为 base，仅改 extra_form_data。",
    "template": {
      "slice_id": "<saved_chart_id>",
      "dashboardId": "<dashboard_id>",
      "datasource": "<copied_from_saved_chart>",
      "viz_type": "funnel",
      "metric": "<copied_from_saved_chart>",
      "groupby": "<copied_from_saved_chart>",
      "adhoc_filters": "<copied_from_saved_chart>",
      "row_limit": "<copied_from_saved_chart>",
      "sort_by_metric": "<copied_from_saved_chart>",
      "percent_calculation_type": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "color_scheme": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "show_legend": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "legendOrientation": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "legendMargin": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "label_type": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "tooltip_label_type": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "number_format": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "currency_format": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "show_labels": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "show_tooltip_labels": "<copied_from_saved_chart_if_present>",
      "extra_form_data": {
        "filters": [
          {
            "col": "stage",
            "op": "IN",
            "val": [
              "Lead",
              "Qualified"
            ]
          }
        ],
        "adhoc_filters": [
          {
            "expressionType": "SIMPLE",
            "clause": "WHERE",
            "subject": "region",
            "operator": "IN",
            "comparator": [
              "East"
            ]
          }
        ],
        "custom_form_data": {}
      }
    }
  },
  "preferred_dynamic_container": {
    "field_name": "extra_form_data",
    "description": "第三方 embedding 允许动态传入的上下文容器；后端会在 merge_extra_form_data() 中把它并入实际查询。",
    "append_keys": [
      "adhoc_filters",
      "filters",
      "interactive_groupby",
      "interactive_highlight",
      "interactive_drilldown",
      "custom_form_data"
    ],
    "override_keys_backend_high_confidence": [
      "granularity_sqla",
      "granularity",
      "time_column",
      "time_grain",
      "time_range",
      "time_grain_sqla",
      "relative_start",
      "relative_end"
    ],
    "notes": "Funnel 当前 controlPanel 没有正式时间字段，因此这些 override 键对 Funnel 通常不是主路径。实际最有意义的是 `filters` 和 `adhoc_filters`。"
  },
  "extra_form_data_field_schema": [
    {
      "field_name": "filters",
      "data_type": "array[QueryObjectFilterClause]",
      "behavior": "append",
      "safe_for_funnel": true,
      "recommended": true,
      "sample_data": [
        {
          "col": "stage",
          "op": "IN",
          "val": [
            "Lead",
            "Qualified"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "effect": "追加 simple filters；后端会转成额外过滤条件。对 Funnel 来说，这也是 `utils/eventHandlers.ts` 交互筛选明确产出的容器。",
      "source": "superset/constants.py + superset/utils/core.py + plugin-chart-echarts/utils/eventHandlers.ts"
    },
    {
      "field_name": "adhoc_filters",
      "data_type": "array[AdhocFilter]",
      "behavior": "append",
      "safe_for_funnel": true,
      "recommended": true,
      "sample_data": [
        {
          "expressionType": "SIMPLE",
          "clause": "WHERE",
          "subject": "region",
          "operator": "IN",
          "comparator": [
            "East"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "effect": "追加 adhoc filters；后端会标记为 `isExtra` 并并入查询。",
      "source": "superset/constants.py + superset/utils/core.py"
    },
    {
      "field_name": "custom_form_data",
      "data_type": "object",
      "behavior": "append",
      "safe_for_funnel": true,
      "recommended": false,
      "sample_data": {},
      "effect": "可传非标准附加数据；Funnel 默认 buildQuery / transformProps 不直接消费它。",
      "source": "superset/constants.py + frontend QueryFormData.ts"
    },
    {
      "field_name": "time_range",
      "data_type": "string",
      "behavior": "override",
      "safe_for_funnel": false,
      "recommended": false,
      "sample_data": "Last 30 days",
      "effect": "这是通用 extra_form_data override 字段，但 Funnel 当前 controlPanel 不以时间字段为主，通常没有必要在 guest embedding 中依赖它。",
      "source": "superset/constants.py + frontend QueryFormData.ts",
      "status": "低相关，不建议在 guest embedding 中依赖"
    }
  ],
  "minimal_extra_form_data_template": {
    "filters": [
      {
        "col": "stage",
        "op": "IN",
        "val": [
          "Lead"
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "recommended_extra_form_data_template": {
    "filters": [
      {
        "col": "stage",
        "op": "IN",
        "val": [
          "Lead",
          "Qualified"
        ]
      }
    ],
    "adhoc_filters": [
      {
        "expressionType": "SIMPLE",
        "clause": "WHERE",
        "subject": "region",
        "operator": "IN",
        "comparator": [
          "East"
        ]
      }
    ],
    "custom_form_data": {}
  },
  "unsafe_root_form_data_changes": [
    {
      "field_name": "slice_id",
      "reason": "与保存态图表 id 不一致会被后端立即判定为请求了另一张图。"
    },
    {
      "field_name": "metric",
      "reason": "它会进入 query_context.queries[*].metrics，并且在 `sort_by_metric=true` 时还会进入 `orderby`。guest 模式下不应在根层修改。"
    },
    {
      "field_name": "groupby",
      "reason": "它会进入 query_context.queries[*].columns，也决定交互筛选最终使用哪些列。guest 模式下不应在根层修改。"
    },
    {
      "field_name": "sort_by_metric",
      "reason": "它会改变 query_context 是否写入 `orderby`，因此属于高敏感查询字段。"
    },
    {
      "field_name": "datasource",
      "reason": "embedded guest 不应改图表绑定数据集。"
    },
    {
      "field_name": "viz_type",
      "reason": "embedded guest 不应把已分享图表改成另一种图。"
    }
  ],
  "practical_guidance": {
    "best_practice": [
      "先从保存态 Funnel 图表读取完整 form_data。",
      "根层字段保持不变，尤其保留 `metric`、`groupby` 和 `sort_by_metric`。",
      "只在 extra_form_data 中放动态 `filters` / `adhoc_filters`。",
      "如果你的嵌入页只是需要做阶段联动筛选，优先使用 `extra_form_data.filters`。"
    ],
    "avoid": [
      "不要在 guest embedding 请求里手工重写 `metric`、`groupby` 或 `sort_by_metric`。",
      "不要把 runtime camelCase 字段名当成 API root 键名使用。",
      "不要把当前 UI 没有正式暴露的 `sort`、`orient`、`gap`、`labelLine`、`legendType` 当成新的 embedding 动态参数。"
    ]
  }
}
